    "**Android Phone** and **Android Tablet** — generic frames that flex to match the aspect ratio of any dropped screenshot." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Android Phone** und **Android Tablet** – generische Rahmen, die sich an das Seitenverhältnis jedes abgelegten Screenshots anpassen."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Téléphone Android** et **Tablette Android** : cadres génériques qui s'adaptent au format de toute capture d'écran déposée."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Android Phone** および **Android Tablet** — ドロップされたスクリーンショットのアスペクト比に合わせて柔軟になる汎用フレーム。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Android 휴대폰** 및 **Android 태블릿** — 드롭된 스크린샷의 가로세로 비율에 맞게 조정되는 일반 프레임입니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Telefone Android** e **Tablet Android** — quadros genéricos que são flexíveis para corresponder à proporção de qualquer captura de tela perdida."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Android 手机** 和 **Android 平板电脑** — 可弯曲以匹配任何掉落屏幕截图的纵横比的通用框架。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "**Android Phone**, **Abstract Pixel 9**, and **Android Tablet** — abstract frames that flex to match the aspect ratio of dropped screenshots." : {

    },
    "**Angular**: a sweep gradient rotating around the center." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Winkelförmig**: ein um die Mitte rotierender Sweep-Gradient."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Angulaire** : un dégradé de balayage tournant autour du centre."
