    "In a non-base language, edits are saved as **per-language overrides** — they don't change the base language." : {

    },
    "In a non-base language, edits to text shapes are saved as **per-language overrides** — they don't change the base." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "In einer Nicht-Basissprache werden Änderungen an Textformen als **Sprachüberschreibungen** gespeichert – die Basis wird dadurch nicht geändert."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dans une langue autre que la langue de base, les modifications apportées aux formes de texte sont enregistrées en tant que **remplacements par langue** : elles ne modifient pas la base."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "基本言語以外の場合、テキスト図形の編集は **言語ごとのオーバーライド**として保存されます。基本言語は変更されません。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "기본 언어가 아닌 경우 텍스트 모양에 대한 편집 내용은 **언어별 재정의**로 저장되며 기본 언어는 변경되지 않습니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Em um idioma não base, as edições nas formas de texto são salvas como **substituições por idioma** — elas não alteram a base."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在非基础语言中，对文本形状的编辑将保存为**每种语言覆盖** - 它们不会更改基础语言。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "In Blank mode, pick the device categories you want — each one becomes a row with the right default screenshot size for the App Store / Play Store." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Wählen Sie im leeren Modus die gewünschten Gerätekategorien aus – jede wird zu einer Zeile mit der richtigen Standard-Screenshot-Größe für den App Store / Play Store."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En mode Vide, choisissez les catégories d'appareils souhaitées : chacune d'elles devient une ligne avec la bonne taille de capture d'écran par défaut pour le App Store/Play Store."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "空白モードでは、必要なデバイス カテゴリを選択します。それぞれが App Store / Play ストアの適切なデフォルトのスクリーンショット サイズを持つ行になります。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "공백 모드에서 원하는 기기 카테고리를 선택하세요. 각 카테고리는 App Store / Play 스토어에 적합한 기본 스크린샷 크기가 포함된 행이 됩니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "No modo em branco, escolha as categorias de dispositivos desejadas – cada uma se torna uma linha com o tamanho de captura de tela padrão correto para App Store / Play Store."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在空白模式下，选择您想要的设备类别 - 每个类别都会成为一行，并具有 App Store/Play 商店的正确默认屏幕截图尺寸。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "In Screenshot Bro: **Settings ▸ App Store Connect**, paste the Issuer ID and Key ID, and import the `.p8` file." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Fügen Sie in Screenshot Bro: **Einstellungen ▸ App Store Connect** die Dateien Issuer ID und Key ID ein und importieren Sie die Datei „.p8“."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
